# {{ project_name }} - Developer Guide

This guide helps developers contribute to {{ project_name }} and understand its architecture.

## Development Setup

### Prerequisites

- Node.js 18+
- pnpm 8+
- TypeScript 5+
- Devbox (optional but recommended)

### Getting Started

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone {{ repository_url }}
cd {{ project_slug }}

# Install dependencies
pnpm install

# Run in development mode
pnpm dev

# Build the project
pnpm build

# Run tests
pnpm test
```

### Using Devbox

```bash
# Initialize devbox environment
devbox shell

# Run commands in devbox
devbox run pnpm test
devbox run pnpm build
```

